sql_query.sql: SELECT 1 AS "a" FROM "catalogue_product" INNER JOIN "catalogue_product" T2 ON ("catalogue_product"."parent_id" = T2."id") INNER JOIN "offer_rangeproduct" ON (T2."id" = "offer_rangeproduct"."product_id") WHERE "offer_rangeproduct"."range_id" = 515 LIMIT 1

SELECT 1 AS "a" FROM "catalogue_productclass" INNER JOIN "offer_range_classes" ON ("catalogue_productclass"."id" = "offer_range_classes"."productclass_id") WHERE "offer_range_classes"."range_id" = 515 LIMIT 1

SELECT 1 AS "a" FROM "catalogue_category" INNER JOIN "offer_range_included_categories" ON ("catalogue_category"."id" = "offer_range_included_categories"."category_id") WHERE "offer_range_included_categories"."range_id" = 515 LIMIT 1

SELECT 1 AS "a" FROM "catalogue_product" INNER JOIN "catalogue_product" T2 ON ("catalogue_product"."parent_id" = T2."id") INNER JOIN "offer_range_excluded_products" ON (T2."id" = "offer_range_excluded_products"."product_id") WHERE "offer_range_excluded_products"."range_id" = 515 LIMIT 1

SELECT DISTINCT 1 AS "a" FROM "catalogue_product" INNER JOIN "offer_rangeproduct" ON ("catalogue_product"."id" = "offer_rangeproduct"."product_id") WHERE ("offer_rangeproduct"."range_id" = 515 AND NOT (EXISTS(SELECT 1 AS "a" FROM "offer_range_excluded_products" U1 WHERE (U1."range_id" = 515 AND U1."product_id" = ("catalogue_product"."id")) LIMIT 1)) AND "catalogue_product"."id" = 914) LIMIT 1
